{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 40,
  "title": "第四十章（去用）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "反者道之動，"
    },
    {
      "text": "弱者道之用。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天下萬物生於有，"
    },
    {
      "text": "有生於無。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "反，本也。本者，道之所以動，動生萬物，背之則亡也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "柔弱者，道之所常用，故能常久。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天下萬物皆從天地生，天地有形位，故言生於有也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天地神明，蜎飛蠕動，皆從道生。道無形，故言生於無也。此言本勝於華，弱勝於強，謙虛勝盈滿也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
